Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヤマト : しまった！\N３本目までも…》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ナルト)ソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト 危ない！\N(サクラ)ナルト!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,(シカマル)クッソ！\N(いの)大丈夫なの!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:11.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラの… 意識が…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラが あんなかに いねえなんて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:25.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)フフフ… ソラのヤツ\Nついに はじけやがった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう誰にも止められねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アスマ)カズマ… キサマ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)木遁の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんて破壊力だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,やめろ！ ソラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,影首縛りの術！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:44.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,(シカマル)やはり ダメか！\N(チョウジ)ボクが！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,(チョウジ)ぐぉ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐわぁ～!!\N(シカマル)チョウジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,任せて！ 治療するわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:04.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソ！ いいかげん 目 覚ませ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:18.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アスマ)カズマ！\Nキサマ どうしてなんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:21.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,実の父親のお前が… なぜだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:26.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前は… ただ殺す道具として\Nソラに九尾を植えつけた！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:30.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが どういう意味か\Nわかっているのか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:41.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,すべては義のため…\Nオレは義の中で ソラを生かす！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,(リー)ボクが行きます！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,(キバ)野郎！\N(赤丸)ワンワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,牙通牙!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,キサマに もはや 義などない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:23.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの義は 火ノ国が\N火ノ国としてあればいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:27.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,その過程は問題ではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 子供の…\Nソラの義は どうなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:36.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,フッ… お前に…\N三代目火影の息子として➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前に どんな義があった？\Nオレは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:44.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレも玉を守った。\Nお前も玉を守った。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,それで いいではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:53.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,確かに… 確かに\Nオレは 玉を守っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:57.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが それは お前の\N考えているような玉ではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:01.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハハ！ 言ったな！\Nお前も そうなんじゃないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:04.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,玉が何だろうと どうでもいい。\Nしょせん オレたちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,玉を守るしかない\Nただの歩ということだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:12.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)だがな 歩じゃ守れんのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから ソラに なってもらった。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:19.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,歩を敵陣に進め\N今 まさに と金となったのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:28.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,子供たちは\N玉を守る歩なんかじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:32.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうでもいい！\Nオレたちが駒である以上➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,どちらかの玉を\N取り合うしかないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,その過程は問題じゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:45.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,盤を ひっくり返してでも\Nオレは勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,(シカマル/チョウジ)うわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,木遁の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:22.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,(キバ)うお～！ うわっ！\N(チョウジ)うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:27.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,((なんで よそ者に…！\Nよそ者じゃねえんだよ コイツは。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ班の仲間だからな))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:35.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,同じじゃねえかよ… ソラ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,なぁ 思い出せよ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,あのときも\Nこうやって バカみてえにさ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:46.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,暴れるお前を止めようとして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,しようがねえよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,おら～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,やったか!?\Nナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:17.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,うわ～！ あ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:26.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:33.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ！ 戻ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:38.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,いるんだろ？ そこに！ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:59.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,もうやめて！\Nソラから離れるんだ ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:12.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,おい ソラ 戻ってきやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ… お前…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,なに!?\Nえっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,ど どういうことだってばよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:39.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,これ 九尾のチャクラが 勝手に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,《今だ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:48.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,火影式耳順術！ 廓庵入鄽垂手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？\Nいつもとは違う…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは… 外部から…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:15.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソ！ 出てくるなってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,な… なんで!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:34.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 偶然ってヤツは ホントに\Nおかしな いたずらをしやがる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,フウカが言っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:48.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,((フウカ : フリド… 私が相手してた\Nあのツンツン頭の子だけどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,(何か ソラと\Nあるんじゃないかしらね…))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:58.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤツとソラは つながっていると…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,もともとは 同じチャクラの九尾。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:07.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフフ… ソラの九尾の怒りに\N本家の九尾が共鳴してるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アスマ)なに!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:16.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフフ… ハハハ！\Nおもしれえじゃねえかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,今度は 本当の人柱力➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:22.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや 九尾の化け狐が発動して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:27.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,再び 里を壊滅させるんだ。\Nハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,《チクショウ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,(九尾)フフフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:51.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:05.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,よせってばよ！ やめろ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,まさか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,(チョウジ)な… 何 これ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは まずいぞ！\Nみんな 逃げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:16.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん… うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:20.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ 目を覚ませ！ おい!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハハ！ いいぞ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)\Nそのまま木ノ葉を ぶっつぶせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。\Nナルト!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,九尾の野郎なんかに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,飲まれてたまるか!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:01.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,こ… これは!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:04.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいぞ！ その調子だ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,クッ… オレは… 呼んでねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,引っ込んでろ 化け狐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:20.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,勝手に ノコノコ 出てくんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤマト隊長\Nなんとかならないんですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:26.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや 今のナルトには\Nボクの術は届かない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:30.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,あとは ナルトの精神力に\Nかけるしかないんだ。\Nでも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:35.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ… クソッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:40.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,(九尾)ワシにまかせろ 小僧。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,断るってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは 逃げねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,化け狐なんかにゃ\N取り込まれねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト。\Nナルト君。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:23.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは… 誓ったんだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,こんなところで こんなことで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前に飲み込まれるわけには\Nいかねえんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:35.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラに説教した オレが\N同じことやるわけには いかねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:40.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,(九尾)フハハハハ…！ 何を遠慮する。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,いつものように言ってみろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:46.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,「お前の力を貸せ」と。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:55.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは この手で\Nお前を引き戻してやるぞ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:19.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。\N(ソラ)誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:26.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,戻ってこい!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:32.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,こっちに来い！\Nお前なぁ いつまで寝てんだよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:35.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいかげん 目を覚ませ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,起きやがれ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:54.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:09.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)\N誰だ？ 誰だ そこにいるのは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだ オレだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:17.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,幼いときのオレ いつも泣いてたオレ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,ひとりぼっちの オレ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:27.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,誰だ？ 誰の声だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:43.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱり… やっぱり そうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:46.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,何も変わっちゃいねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:49.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは ひとりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:52.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:43.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,待ってろ… 今 助けてやるから。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:55.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,待ってろ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:03.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)誰の声だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:35.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,今日は ナルトの\N九尾発動の記録を振り返るわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトの九尾のチャクラが\N初めて発動したのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:41.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,波の国の任務で白と戦ったとき。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,この頃は\N意識して使うというより➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:46.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,感情の高ぶりを きっかけに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふいに出る\Nというものだったみたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,初めて 自分の意志で使ったのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:54.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,自来也様との修行を経て\Nガマブン太を呼んだときね。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,その後\N中忍試験で ネジさんを倒したり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:02.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉崩しで守鶴となった\N我愛羅さんと戦ったり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,呪印の力を借りた\Nサスケ君との戦いのときも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:09.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,奥の手として 九尾のチャクラは\Nナルトのピンチを救ってきたの。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:14.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも 九尾の力に頼った強さは\N本当の強さじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:17.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,頼りすぎれば 仲間を傷つけ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,自分自身をも傷つけてしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,だからこそ ナルトは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:25.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,自分自身の力で ソラを救おうと\Nこんなにも がんばっているのね。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no! It's his third tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:08.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,, {\i1}Resonance\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Naruto! Look out!\N- Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Damn it...!\N- Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Sora's consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:15.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Sora's not in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:27.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora has flipped at last.\NNobody can stop him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma... You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Style Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Such destructive force...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Strangle Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- I knew it wouldn't work!\N- Let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.\NI'll heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma... Why did you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You are his real father... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:26.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You implanted the Nine-Tails in Sora\Nin order to use him as a tool for killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all for my will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:40.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I will put him to good use\Nfor my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Fang Over Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have\Na cause left to speak of!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:23.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to make sure\Nthe Land of Fire stays as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about your child's...\NSora's dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:38.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your dream as\Nthe son of the Third Hokage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I protected the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:46.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And you did, too.\NIsn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:53.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed... I'm protecting a king...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:57.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not the king\Nyou've got in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.\NIt's the same with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who the king is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When all is said and done,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,we're just pawns and\Nall we can do is protect the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:12.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But a pawn isn't strong enough\Nto protect a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I turned Sora\Ninto what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:18.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster pawn that has advanced\Ninto enemy territory to take out your king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:27.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Children aren't pawns\Nfor protecting a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:36.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're pieces,\Nall we can do is take the other's king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How it's done isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:42.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you somehow\Nturned the board around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd still win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Style Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why side with an outsider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:30.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's not an outsider.\N{\i1}He's a member of Team Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Remember, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:42.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you acted like an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and I tried to stop you from thrashing\Nabout like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did he get him?!\N- Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:34.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Come back!\NI know you're in there, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Sora... Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- What...?!\N- Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:39.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nine-Tails Chakra, by itself...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:48.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,STABILIZE\N\N\N{\i1}Hokage Style: Elder Jutsu!\N{\i1}10th Edict on Enlightenment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming...from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:15.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Don't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidence sure plays\Nfunny tricks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Fouka said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:47.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furido... About that kid with\N{\i1}the pointy hair I fought against...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:52.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if he might kind of\N{\i1}be like Sora somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,She said he and Sora\Nmight be connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Chakra from\Nthe same Nine-Tails after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:07.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The rage of Sora's Nine-Tails is\Nresonating with the real Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:19.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this interesting?!\NNow the true Jinchuriki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:22.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Nine-Tailed monster fox\Nwill be set in motion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and once again destroy the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:52.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this...!\NStop, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:27.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good!\NRun, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Wake up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash the Hidden Leaf to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:59.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I going to let\Nthe Nine-Tails jerk take me over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice! Keep it up, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:14.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't call you...!\NBeat it, monster fox...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:20.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just show up on your own...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato,\Ncan't something be done about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No. My Jutsu won't work\Non Naruto now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:30.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only have faith\Nin his mental strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:34.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me...boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be overtaken by\Nthe likes of a monster fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a vow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:30.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not...be...taken over...\Nby you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:35.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not do the same thing\NI lectured Sora about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hesitate?\NJust say it like always!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:46.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Loan me your power."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:55.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'll get you back\Nwith my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:58.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17: